plot: The crew is in Amsterdam for a Paper Boi concert, which ends up being cancelled due to an age old local tradition. Van and Darius go on an adventure which takes them to a bizarre funeral.

Earn, Alfred, Darius and Van head out to Amsterdam to get ready for Alfred/Paper Boi's concert. He ends up refusing to perform after checking out the crowd and Earn agrees. The crew ends up getting directions to a mansion where Tupac's funeral is being held.
